{
  "stem": "15732.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they took to an assembly platz-- place-- that was usually on a-- on a soccer field, on a place where in the vicinity of the railway.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the people were all put on the railway and off over the Dniester.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After that incident, well, I can remember that we were extremely fearful that the next time, we will be taken.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a group in Czernowitz who organized-- that means, to organize means to give money, in Romania-- a-- a-- a certain lawyer, Romanian lawyer, was sent to Bucharest to try to find some way of assuring the security of all those Polish citizens.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In-- when the war-- when the-- when there was the-- the agreement between Russia and Germany to divide Poland, the Polish official government fled to Romania.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On their way to Bucharest, they had to pass Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that means that they were, for maybe a few days, in Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they rested.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they continued to Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In Romania, they established a provisional government-- Polish government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, the trick was that this government was under the-- I forgot how you say it in English.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In Hebrew, it's [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That is, they-- they were under protection-- I suppose would be the nearest word-- under the protection of the Swiss government that protected all those Polish citizens, officials, that fled.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "What we really aimed to do is to get the same documents from the Swiss consul that we are protected by them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because of my father being Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- we had a Polish passport, Polish-- my father had-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where he was born--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and really, he came back that-- the lawyer came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the sum of money was quite high.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother was very concerned.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
